3-nested-loop sql    [包含3个及以上nested-loop的sql]

SQL_ID CHILD_NUMBER NL_CNT PARSING_SCHEMA_NAME SQL_FULLTEXT
98fpsr3hq09sg 0 47 NBPF_SQ SELECT SUM(CNT) FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM USER_INDEXES WHERE STATUS = 'UNUSABLE' AND TABLE_NAME = :B2 AND INDEX_NAME = :B1 UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM USER_IND_PARTITIONS A, USER_INDEXES B WHERE A.INDEX_NAME = B.INDEX_NAME AND A.STATUS = 'UNUSABLE' AND B.TABLE_NAME = :B2 AND A.INDEX_NAME = :B1 UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM USER_IND_PARTITIONS A, USER_INDEXES B WHERE A.INDEX_NAME = B.INDEX_NAME AND A.STATUS = 'UNUSABLE' AND B.TABLE_NAME = :B2 AND A.INDEX_NAME = :B1 )
